<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Aloop Offroad</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= favicon_link_tag %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-32x32.png" sizes="32x32">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-16x16.png" sizes="16x16">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
  <link rel="mask-icon" href="/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#5bbad5">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora:400,700|Roboto:400,900" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>



<!-- MENU GOES HERE -->
<div id="main-nav" class="navbar navbar-default navbar-static-top" role="navigation">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <%= link_to root_path, class: "navbar-brand" do %>
            <%= image_tag "masterlogoSQ.png", style: "margin: -50px 0 0 20px; height: 120px" %>
          <% end %>
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-menubuilder"><span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span><span class="icon-bar"></span><span class="icon-bar"></span><span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-menubuilder">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-left">
                <li><%= link_to home_export_path do %><p class="inner">Kits</p><% end %></li>
                <li><%= link_to home_export_path do %><p class="inner">Gallery</p><% end %></li>
                <li><%= link_to home_export_path do %><p class="inner">Store</p><% end %></li>
                <li><%= link_to home_info_path do %><p class="inner">Info</p><% end %></li>
                <li><%= link_to home_export_path do %><p class="inner">Contact</p><% end %></li>
                <li><%= link_to home_export_path do %><p class="inner">Export</p><% end %></li>
                <% if current_user %>
                  <li><%= link_to user_path(current_user) do %><p class="inner">My Account</p><% end %></li>
                <% else %>
                  <li><%= link_to new_user_session_path do %><p class="inner">Login</p><% end %></li>
                <% end %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="main-nav-background"></div>

  <% if flash[:notice] %>
    <div class="alert alert-success">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
    </div>
  <% elsif flash.now[:alert] %>
    <div class="alert alert-danger">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
      <%= flash.now[:alert] %>
    </div>
  <% elsif flash[:alert] %>
    <div class="alert alert-warning">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
      <%= flash[:alert] %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  
<%= yield %>

<footer>
  <div class="row text-center footer-stripe">
    <h1>Aloop Offroad</h1>
    <h3>Unique Performance Prducts</h3>
  </div> <!-- title -->

  <div class="row tri-row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <h2 class="text-center">Questions</h2>
      <p>If you really, really have to talk to a human being, then call Pete on his cell phone (<a href="tel:1-303-550-2582">+1 303-550-2582</a>) and leave a message.</p>
      <p>(He's the closest thing to a human being that we have here).</p>
      <p>Pete will get back to you as soon as possible, usually on the same day you call.</p>
    </div> <!-- triple thingy one -->

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <h2 class="text-center">Contact Aloop</h2>
      <p>We might not keep regular office hours, but your business is still very important to us.</p>
      <p>Please contact us by postal service, <a href="mailto:sales@aloop.com">email</a>. We will attempt to respond to all inquiries within 24 hours.</p>
      <p>We are located in the USA Mountain Time Zone (GMT-7hrs).</p>
    </div> <!-- triple thingy one -->

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <h2 class="text-center">Overseas Orders</h2>
      <p>Overseas orders are no problem!</p>
      <p>We've sold thousands of our Aloop 4SMX kits to customers in over 40 countries! Most shipments are sent via US Mail Global Express Mail, and can arrive in under 1 week, no matter where in the world you live.</p>
    </div> <!-- triple thingy one -->
  </div> <!-- triple thingy row -->

  <div class="row text-center" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <p><a href="mailto:sales@aloop.com">sales@aloop.com</a>  |  PO Box 412, Sedalia, CO 80135, USA | <a href="www.aloop.com">www.aloop.com</a></p>
  </div> <!-- title -->


</footer>

</body>
</html>
